  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Light, sparse, short decay on all voices with generous reverb space. Very short decays (0.03–0.18s) make each hit a brief transient event that dissolves into the reverb tail before the next hit arrives. The result is a rain-like percussion texture — impacts separated by silence, each impact leaving a diffused reverb trace. The grid disappears. Only presence remains.",
